cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object detection and proposes a new method to improve the performance of object detectors. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the proposed method involves decoupling the classification and regression tasks, which is a machine learning technique. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of AI models for object detection. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper involves designing a new architecture for object detection models. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of multimedia models for object detection.
